org.openimaj.lsh.sketch

Class IntLSHSketcher<OBJECT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.lsh.sketch.IntLSHSketcher<OBJECT>
  • Type Parameters:
    OBJECT - Type of object being sketched
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sketcher<OBJECT,int[]>

    public class IntLSHSketcher<OBJECT>
extends Object
implements Sketcher<OBJECT,int[]>
    A Sketcher that produces bit-string sketches encoded as int arrays. Only the least-significant bit of each hash function will be appended to the final sketch. The length of the output array will be computed such that the bit from each hash function is contained.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
